{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 {\b Problem}: AI provides subpar solutions or fails to resolve the issue.\line {\b Solution}: Ask AI, \u8220"What specific information or data is needed to fix this problem?\u8221"\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 {\b Problem}: AI stumbles on multi-layered tasks requiring decomposition into manageable steps.\line {\b Solution}: Hint AI, \u8220"Please break down this problem into a series of step-by-step actions.\u8221"\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 {\b Problem}: Initial AI-generated responses may sometimes lack depth, precision, or full alignment with user expectations.\line {\b Solution}: Use this prompt after the first answer: \u8220"Revise and improve your response to the prompt.\u8221"\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 {\b Problem}: AI lacks understanding of the project\u8217's core or file system layout.\line {\b Solution}: Create WIKI page with project overview, its structure, and aims. Hint AI:\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \u8220"Analyze this project documentation at:\u8221" - https://company.com/solution/wiki/home.md - C:.wiki.md\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 {\b Problem}: AI develops solutions that don\u8217't align with the environment or project technology stack.\line {\b Solution}: Hint AI:\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \u8220"Analyze these resources for a bespoke solution:\u8221" - Solution File: C:.Solution.sln - Project File: C:.Solution.Project.csproj - Coding Standards: C:.editorconfig\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 {\b Problem}: AI generates code that\u8217's hard to understand or maintain.\line {\b Solution}: Supply AI with examples of well-documented company code from previous projects. Hint AI:\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \u8220"Refer to these examples of clean and well-documented code for crafting your solution:\u8221" - Repository Link: https://company.com/solution/repo/clean-code-examples - Local Directory: C:-code-examples\par}
